---
import ToolLayout from "../../layouts/ToolLayout.astro";

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "Do tags still matter for YouTube video SEO?",
    answer:
      "Yes, tags help YouTube's algorithm understand the context, content, and category of your video. While titles, descriptions, and thumbnails are primary factors, tags are crucial for ranking in search, sidebar recommendations, and capturing common typos.",
  },
  {
    question: "What is the character limit for YouTube video tags?",
    answer:
      "YouTube limits tags to a total of 500 characters across all tags combined. It is best to use 10 to 18 highly relevant tags that stay within this limit rather than stuffing unrelated words.",
  },
  {
    question: "How should I structure my video tags?",
    answer:
      "Use your main focus keyword as the first tag (e.g. 'how to make money online'). Follow it with 3-5 long-tail variations, 2-3 broader category tags (e.g. 'finance', 'business'), and common spelling variations or target keywords.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can I use tags from this generator for YouTube Shorts?",
    answer:
      "Yes. Toggling the 'Include Shorts Tags' option appends popular short-form video tags like #Shorts, youtube shorts, shorts feed, and trending short-form tags to help search indexes category placement.",
  },
];
---

<ToolLayout
  title="YouTube Tag Generator - Free Video SEO Tags Generator"
  description="Generate highly relevant SEO tags for your YouTube videos and Shorts. Free AI YouTube tag generator tool with custom category filters."
  toolName="YouTube Tag Generator"
  toolDescription="Optimize your YouTube video SEO. Enter your video title or focus keyword, select a category, and generate copy-pasteable metadata tags instantly."
  category="Writing Tools"
  faqs={faqs}
>
  <div slot="calculator" class="calc-card glass">
    <div class="calc-grid" id="calc-form-container">
      <!-- Input fields -->
      <form class="calc-form" id="tag-form" onsubmit="return false;">
        <div class="form-group">
          <div class="label-header">
            <label for="video-title" class="icon-label">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="field-icon"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M5.25 5.653c0-.856.917-1.398 1.667-.986l11.54 6.347a1.125 1.125 0 0 1 0 1.972l-11.54 6.347c-.75.412-1.667-.13-1.667-.986V5.653Z"
                ></path>
              </svg>
              Video Title or Focus Keyword
            </label>
          </div>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="video-title"
            class="form-input"
            placeholder="e.g., How to start freelance copywriting"
            required
          />
        </div>

        <div class="form-row-2">
          <div class="form-group">
            <div class="label-header">
              <label for="video-category" class="icon-label">
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="1.5"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  class="field-icon"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M9.568 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25v4.318c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591l9.581 9.581a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 1.591 0l4.318-4.318a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 0-1.591L9.568 3.659A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 7.977 3Z"
                  ></path>
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M6 7.5h.008v.008H6V7.5Z"></path>
                </svg>
                Video Category
              </label>
            </div>
            <select id="video-category" class="form-input">
              <option value="tech">Tech, Hardware & Tutorials</option>
              <option value="cooking">Cooking, Food & Recipes</option>
              <option value="gaming">Gaming Walkthroughs & Gameplay</option>
              <option value="finance" selected
                >Business, Finance & Marketing</option
              >
              <option value="fitness">Fitness, Gym & Workout</option>
              <option value="general">General Vlog / Educational</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div
            class="form-group"
            style="justify-content: center; margin-top: 1rem;"
          >
            <label class="checkbox-container">
              <input type="checkbox" id="include-shorts" />
              <span class="checkbox-label">Include Shorts Tags (#Shorts)</span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="form-actions">
          <button
            type="button"
            id="calc-submit-btn"
            class="calc-btn"
            style="width: 100%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.5rem;"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke="currentColor"
              style="width: 18px; height: 18px;"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M9.813 15.904L9 21l8.982-8.982M18 13.636l.764-5.097L9.82 17.5M9.813 15.904L9 21l8.982-8.982"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            Generate Video Tags
          </button>
          <button
            type="button"
            id="calc-reset-btn"
            class="calc-btn-secondary"
            style="width: 100%;">Reset</button
          >
        </div>
      </form>

      <!-- Outputs Display -->
      <div class="calc-results" id="results-wrapper">
        <div class="empty-state text-center" id="res-empty-box">
          <svg
            class="empty-icon"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            fill="none"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            stroke-width="1.5"
            stroke="currentColor"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              d="M9.568 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25v4.318c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591l9.581 9.581a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 1.591 0l4.318-4.318a1.125 1.125 0 0 0 0-1.591L9.568 3.659A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 7.977 3Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <h3>Awaiting Video Keywords</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Enter your video title or main topic, then click Generate to
            construct optimized metadata tags.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="results-active hidden" id="res-active-box">
          <div class="rate-range-box">
            <h4 class="rate-label">Generated Tags Count</h4>
            <div class="rate-range" id="res-tags-count">0 Tags</div>
            <div class="grade-badge grade-low" id="res-char-count">
              0 / 500 Characters
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="breakdown-box">
            <div
              style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
            >
              <h4 class="breakdown-title" style="margin: 0;">
                Click a tag to remove it:
              </h4>
              <button
                type="button"
                id="copy-tags-btn"
                class="copy-pitch-btn"
                style="color: var(--color-brand); font-weight: 700; border: none; background: transparent; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  style="width: 16px; height: 16px;"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M15.75 17.25v3.375c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-9.75a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V7.875c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H5.25M16.5 5.25h.008v.008H16.5V5.25Zm-3 0h.008v.008h-.008V5.25Zm-3 0h.008v.008h-.008V5.25Zm-3 0h.008v.008h-.008V5.25Zm-3 0h.008v.008h-.008V5.25ZM9 10.5c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h9.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v10.5c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-9.75a1.125 1.125 0 0 1-1.125-1.125V10.5Z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
                Copy Tags
              </button>
            </div>

            <div id="tags-chips-wrapper" class="tags-chips-container">
              <!-- Slotted tags dynamic chips -->
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div slot="about">
    <h2>How to Generate Tags for Youtube Videos</h2>
    <div
      style="margin: 1.5rem 0; background: var(--color-bg-alt); padding: 1.25rem; border-radius: var(--radius-md); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-left: 4px solid var(--color-brand);"
    >
      <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.95rem;">
        💡 <strong>Want to master video SEO?</strong> Read our comprehensive guide
        on <a
          href="/blog/youtube-tag-generator-guide"
          style="color: var(--color-brand); text-decoration: underline;"
          >YouTube Video Tags & Channel Growth Strategies</a
        > to learn how to write tags that rank, structure titles for CTR, and optimize
        descriptions for search algorithms.
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>
      Optimizing video metadata is critical to ranking in search feeds and
      suggested sidebar columns. This **free youtube tag generator tool**
      automates tag harvesting. Sourcing highly relevant terms from user inputs
      and filtering them within character thresholds ensures your listings
      remain compliant.
    </p>

    <div class="step-guide">
      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 1: Enter Video Topic or Focus Keyword</h3>
        <p>
          Type your primary title in the input box. Our **ai youtube video tag
          generator** will extract the core nouns and long-tail topics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 2: Choose Video Category</h3>
        <p>
          Select your category dropdown. This structures the broad tags (e.g.
          'gaming setup', 'recipe' or 'coding tutorial') to anchor the video's
          theme.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 3: Toggle Shorts Filters</h3>
        <p>
          If you are uploading a short video, tick the **tags for youtube shorts
          generator** checkbox to append trending short-form tags (#Shorts,
          shorts feed).
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="step-item">
        <h3>Step 4: Prune and Copy Tags</h3>
        <p>
          Click generate. You can click on any generated tag chip to delete it
          if it is irrelevant. Then click **Copy Tags** to copy the
          comma-separated string straight to YouTube Studio.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Generate Best Tags for Youtube Videos</h2>
    <p>
      Using a structured **seo tags generator for youtube** provides key
      technical features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>AI-Generated Title Expansion:</strong> Takes your short title and
        expands it into semantic search alternatives automatically.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Interactive Chip Control:</strong> Gives you full control over the
        final list, letting you click to delete tags.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>500-Character Threshold Tracker:</strong> Tracks character counts
        dynamically so you never exceed YouTube's maximum limit.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Niche Templates:</strong> Access pre-built lists matching different
        industries.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Benefits of Using the Best Free YouTube Tag Generator</h2>
    <p>
      Leveraging this **free ai youtube tag generator** and **ai tags generator
      for youtube** offers several benefits:
    </p>
    <ol
      style="margin-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.25rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);"
    >
      <li>
        <strong>Saves Time:</strong> Generates 15-20 highly relevant tag variations
        in seconds.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Improves Discoverability:</strong> Targets long-tail search queries
        where competition is lower, driving views.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Boosts Suggested Video Placement:</strong> Matching category tags
